Class VectorClock.Tuple

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.ornl.keva.core.VectorClock.Tuple

    public static class VectorClock.Tuple
extends java.lang.Object
    A clock tuple is a logical clock value consisting of a client identifier and a timestamp.
